Features:

  1. Material: upper vamp: mesh 12A/outsole: MD insole: EVA
  2. Applicable people/age/season: young people/all seasons
  3. Style: casual
  4. Product usage: daily/sport
  • An adaptive, adapts to your foot for a custom-like fit and secure lock-down.
  • Lightweight support with rubber fit with full-length when racing/running/walking.
  • Inspired by feedback from runners craving a shoe fit of a sock with absorb sweat.
  • Beautiful designs for all details, high quality and comfort of youth and vitality.
  • EVA sole, good flexibility, and strong anti-deformation to enhance the cushioning performance and slip resistance.
